      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "The paper does not perform ablation studies on BitterPredict descriptor subgroups. BitterPredict is mentioned as a comparison tool (predicts bitterness from chemical structure using physicochemical descriptors), but no systematic removal or sensitivity analysis of its descriptors is conducted. The paper focuses on developing and validating BitterMasS (mass spectrum-based prediction), not analyzing BitterPredict's internal descriptor sensitivity.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1021-acs-jafc-3c09767",
