      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "The paper does not perform descriptor-group ablation testing on BitterPredict or any structure-based classifier. The paper trains and interprets BitterMasS, which uses mass-spectral features (m/z bins and instrument parameters), not chemical structure descriptors. The interpretability method used is Random Forest feature importance, not ablation testing.",
