      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The feature importance values are relative and should be interpreted in the context of the other features in the model. Since the total importance of all features is equal to one, the values of each feature were expressed as a percentage and the 20 most important features are presented in Figure 3.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper ranks features by importance (Figure 3), but uses Random Forest feature importance ranking, not ablation testing. The outcome (ranked features) is similar, but the method is different.",
