      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "The paper does not perform ablation studies. Feature importance is extracted post-hoc from the trained Random Forest model (passage 8), not by removing descriptor subgroups and retraining or re-evaluating.",
